I found a (little) bug in zsh.

taifun% echo $ZSH_VERSION
2.6-beta13
taifun% PATH=/usr/ucb:/usr/bin:/bin
taifun% echo $PATH[1,(ws.:.)-2]
/usr/ucb:/usr/bi

I would expect the answer
/usr/ucb:/usr/bin

